# Project Structure Overview

This repository contains the Hugo site for Appraisily's article subdomain, featuring modular content generation with AI capabilities.

## Key Directories

- [content/](mdc:content/) - Contains all article content directories with Markdown files and research data
- [layouts/](mdc:layouts/) - Contains HTML templates and shortcodes for rendering content
  - [layouts/shortcodes/](mdc:layouts/shortcodes/) - Custom shortcodes for content modules
  - [layouts/_default/](mdc:layouts/_default/) - Base templates for the site
  - [layouts/partials/](mdc:layouts/partials/) - Reusable HTML components
- [static/](mdc:static/) - Static assets like CSS, JavaScript, and images
- [scripts/](mdc:scripts/) - Utility scripts for content generation and site management

## Key Configuration Files

- [config.toml](mdc:config.toml) - Main Hugo configuration file
- [netlify.toml](mdc:netlify.toml) - Netlify deployment configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - NPM package configuration with scripts for development

